56
00:03:07,291 --> 00:03:09,085
-What? Seven years old?
-Yeah.

57
00:03:09,961 --> 00:03:10,795
Oh my.

58
00:03:13,881 --> 00:03:15,341
Ta-da.

59
00:03:27,979 --> 00:03:28,896
Let's see.

60
00:03:29,897 --> 00:03:31,524
It says 2018!

61
00:03:31,607 --> 00:03:33,026
-It really is seven years old.
-Seriously?

62
00:03:33,109 --> 00:03:34,694
-Yeah.
-It's totally fine.

63
00:03:34,777 --> 00:03:35,611
No, don't…

64
00:03:35,695 --> 00:03:36,863
-Really?
-What the heck?

65
00:03:36,946 --> 00:03:39,032
